#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:606
msgid ""
"Warning: Book metadata location is set to hash-based storage. Writing "
"highlights into a PDF modifies the file which may change the partial hash, "
"resulting in its metadata (e.g., highlights and progress) being unlinked and "
"lost."
msgstr ""
"Opozorilo: Lokacija metapodatkov knjige je nastavljena na shrambo na podlagi "
"zgostitve (hash). Zapisovanje poudarkov v PDF spremeni datoteko, kar lahko "
"spremeni delno zgostitev, zaradi česar se metapodatki (npr. poudarki in "
"napredek) razvežejo in izgubijo."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:612
msgid ""
"Highlights in this document will be saved in the settings file, but they "
"won't be written in the document itself because the file is in a read-only "
"location.\n"
"\n"
"If you wish your highlights to be saved in the document, just move it to a "
"writable directory first."
msgstr ""
"Poudarki v tem dokumentu bodo shranjeni v nastavitveni datoteki, ne bodo pa "
"zapisani v sam dokument, ker je datoteka na lokaciji samo za branje.\n"
"\n"
"Če želiš, da se poudarki shranijo v dokument, ga najprej premakni v mapo, "
"kjer je pisanje dovoljeno."

