msgid "No OCR languages"
msgstr "Ni jezikov za OCR"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:100
msgid "Page Crop"
msgstr "Obrezovanje strani"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:103
msgctxt "Page crop"
msgid "none"
msgstr "brez"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:103
msgctxt "Page crop"
msgid "auto"
msgstr "samodejno"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:103
msgctxt "Page crop"
msgid "semi-auto"
msgstr "pol-samodejno"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:103
msgctxt "Page crop"
msgid "manual"
msgstr "ročno"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:113
msgid ""
"Allows cropping blank page margins in the original document.\n"
"This might be needed on scanned documents, that may have speckles or "
"fingerprints in the margins, to be able to use zoom to fit content width.\n"
"- 'none' does not cut the original document margins.\n"
"- 'auto' finds content area automatically.\n"
"- 'semi-auto\" finds content area automatically, inside some larger area "
"defined manually.\n"
"- 'manual\" uses the area defined manually as-is.\n"
"\n"
"In 'semi-auto' and 'manual' modes, you may need to define areas once on an "
"odd page number, and once on an even page number (these areas will then be "
"used for all odd, or even, page numbers)."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča obrezovanje praznih robov strani v izvirnem dokumentu.\n"
"To je lahko koristno pri skeniranih dokumentih, ki imajo na robovih pike ali "
"prstne odtise, da lahko uporabiš povečavo po širini vsebine.\n"
"- 'brez' ne odreže robov izvirnega dokumenta.\n"
"- 'samodejno' samodejno najde območje vsebine.\n"
"- 'pol-samodejno' samodejno najde vsebino znotraj večjega, ročno določenega "
"območja.\n"
"- 'ročno' uporabi ročno določeno območje takšno, kot je.\n"
"\n"
"V 'pol-samodejnem' in 'ročnem' načinu boš morda moral območje določiti "
"enkrat na lihi in enkrat na sodi strani (ta območja bodo nato uporabljena za "
"vse lihe oziroma sode strani)."

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:124
msgid "Margin"
msgstr "Rob"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:131
msgid "Set margins to be applied after page-crop and zoom modes are applied."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi robove, ki se uveljavijo po obrezovanju strani in uporabi povečave."

