"\n"
"- Za prikaz **ZGORNJEGA** ali **SPODNJEGA MENIJA** klikni na označena "
"območja. Za zgornji meni lahko zgornje območje klikneš ali podrsneš "
"navzdol.\n"
"- Območje **STATUSNE VRSTICE** lahko uporabiš za preklapljanje med elementi "
"vrstice (če je viden en element). Z zaporednimi dotiki lahko vrstico tudi "
"skriješ ali prikažeš.\n"

#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:127
msgid ""
"## User interface tips <a id=\"uitips\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"- You can change the interface language using:\n"
"\n"
"> **Menu ➔ ![Settings](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.settings.svg) ➔ "
"Language**\n"
"\n"
"- If you press both **ScreenKB** + **Press** on an option or menu item (font "
"weight, line spacing etc.), you can set its value as **DEFAULT**.  The new "
"value will only be applied to documents opened from now on. Previously "
"opened documents will keep their settings. You can identify default values "
"as a STAR in menu or as a black border around indicators as seen below:\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-before-avoid\">![Default setting 1](resources/"
"quickstart/defaultsetting1.png)</div>\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-before-avoid\">![Default setting 2](resources/"
"quickstart/defaultsetting2.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- You can see explanations for some items on the **TOP MENU** by pressing "
"both **ScreenKB** + **Press** on the name of the option.\n"
"- You can **CLOSE** full screen dialogs (History, Table of Contents, "
"Bookmarks, Reading Statistics etc.) by pressing the **Back** key.\n"
"- **SCREENSHOTS** can be taken by pressing the **ScreenKB** + **Menu** keys\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-after-avoid\">![Number picker](resources/"
"quickstart/numberpicker.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- In dialogs containing adjustment arrow buttons like the one above, you can "
"use the directional keys to move around. If widgets have menus, pressing the "
"**Menu** key should open them.\n"
"- You can toggle content selection mode by pressing either the **Up** or "
"**Down** keys. The selection tool becomes available so you can select one or "
"multiple words, for either dictionary, wikipedia or text look ups.\n"
"- You can highlight blocks of text by selecting multiple words with the "
"content selection tool.\n"
"- You can move through your document with the **Left** or **Right** cursor "
"keys which, should take you to the previous or next chapter respectively.\n"
"- The content selection tool's sensitivity can be adjusted in the **TOP "
"MENU**.\n"
"\n"
"> **Menu ➔ ![Typesettings](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.typeset.svg) ➔ "
"Selection on text**\n"
msgstr ""
"## Nasveti za uporabo vmesnika <a id=\\\"uitips\\\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"- Jezik vmesnika lahko spremeniš tukaj:\n"
"\n"
"> **Meni ➔ ![Nastavitve](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.settings.svg) ➔ "
"Jezik**\n"
"\n"
"- Če hkrati pritisneš **ScreenKB** + **Press** na kateri koli možnosti  "
"(debelina pisave, razmik med vrsticami itd.), lahko to vrednost nastaviš "
"kot  **PRIVZETO**. Nova vrednost bo veljala le za dokumente, ki jih boš "
"odprl od zdaj naprej. Že odprti dokumenti bodo ohranili svoje nastavitve. "
"Privzete vrednosti prepoznaš po ZVEZDICI v meniju ali po črni obrobi okoli "
"indikatorjev, kot je prikazano spodaj:\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\\\"img-block break-before-avoid\\\">![Default setting 1]"
"(resources/quickstart/defaultsetting1.png)</div>\n"
"<div class=\\\"img-block break-before-avoid\\\">![Default setting 2]"
"(resources/quickstart/defaultsetting2.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- Razlage za nekatere elemente v **ZGORNJEM MENIJU** si lahko ogledaš s "
"hkratnim pritiskom na **ScreenKB** + **Press** na imenu možnosti.\n"
"- Celozaslonska okna (Zgodovina, Kazalo, Zaznamki, Statistika branja itd.) "
"lahko **ZAPREŠ** s pritiskom na tipko **Nazaj**.\n"
"- **ZASLONSKE SLIKE** lahko zajameš s pritiskom na tipki **ScreenKB** + "
"**Menu**.\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-after-avoid\\\">![Izbirnik števil] (resources/"
"quickstart/numberpicker.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- V oknih s puščicami za prilagajanje (kot zgoraj) se lahko premikaš s "
"smernimi tipkami. Če imajo gradniki svoje menije, jih odpreš s pritiskom na "
"tipko **Menu**.\n"
"- Način izbiranja vsebine preklapljaš s tipkama **Gor** ali **Dol**. Ko je "
"orodje aktivno, lahko izbereš eno ali več besed za iskanje v slovarju, "
"Wikipediji ali po besedilu.\n"
"- Dele besedila lahko poudariš tako, da izbereš več besed hkrati.\\n\"\n"
"- Po dokumentu se lahko premikaš s smernima tipkama **Levo** ali **Desno**, "
"ki te popeljeta na prejšnje oziroma naslednje poglavje.\\n\"\n"
"- Občutljivost orodja za izbiranje lahko nastaviš v **ZGORNJEM MENIJU**:\n"
"\n"
"> **Meni ➔ ![Oblikovanje](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.typeset.svg) ➔ "
"Izbiranje besedila**\n"

