#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:181
msgid ""
"## User interface tips <a id=\"uitips\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"- You can change the interface language using:\n"
"\n"
"> **TOP MENU ➔ ![Settings](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.settings.svg) ➔ "
"Language**\n"
"\n"
"- If you tap and hold on an option or menu item (font weight, line spacing "
"etc.), you can set its value as **DEFAULT**.  The new value will only be "
"applied to documents opened from now on. Previously opened documents will "
"keep their settings. You can identify default values as a STAR in menu or as "
"a black border around indicators as seen below:\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-before-avoid\">![Default setting 1](resources/"
"quickstart/defaultsetting1.png)</div>\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-before-avoid\">![Default setting 2](resources/"
"quickstart/defaultsetting2.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- You can see explanations for all items on the **BOTTOM MENU** by tapping "
"and holding the name of the option. This is also available for most of the "
"**TOP MENU** menu items.\n"
"- You can **CLOSE** full screen dialogs (History, Table of Contents, "
"Bookmarks, Reading Statistics etc.) by swiping down\n"
"- **SCREENSHOTS** can be taken by touching opposing corners of the screen "
"diagonally at the same time or by making a long diagonal swipe\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-after-avoid\">![Number picker](resources/"
"quickstart/numberpicker.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- In dialogs containing adjustment arrow buttons like the one above, you can "
"tap and hold on arrow buttons to increase / decrease the value in bigger "
"increments\n"
"- You can **CLOSE** this type of dialog (non-full screen) by tapping outside "
"of the window. You can **MOVE** this type of dialog by holding the window "
"title and dragging\n"
"- You can make this type of dialog **SEMI-TRANSPARENT** (to see the text "
"under it while adjusting a value) by tapping and holding the window title\n"
"- Tapping and holding a word brings up a dialog which allows you to search "
"for the selection to find more occurrences in the document or to look it up "
"on Wikipedia\n"
"- You can highlight sections by tapping and holding a word and dragging your "
"finger\n"
"- You can move through your document via the **SKIM DOCUMENT** dialog:\n"
"\n"
"> **TOP MENU ➔ ![Navigation](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.navigation.svg) "
"➔ Skim document**\n"
msgstr ""
"## Nasveti za uporabo vmesnika <a id=\"uitips\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"- Jezik vmesnika lahko spremeniš tukaj:\n"
"\n"
"> **ZGORNJI MENI ➔ ![Nastavitve](resources/icons/mdlight/"
"appbar.settings.svg) ➔ Jezik**\n"
"\n"
"- Če pritisneš in držiš katero koli možnost (debelina pisave, razmik med "
"vrsticami itd.), jo lahko nastaviš kot **PRIVZETO**. Nova vrednost bo "
"veljala le za dokumente, ki jih boš odprl od zdaj naprej. Že odprti "
"dokumenti bodo ohranili svoje nastavitve. Privzete vrednosti prepoznaš po "
"ZVEZDICI v meniju ali po črni obrobi okoli indikatorjev, kot je prikazano "
"spodaj:\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-before-avoid\">![Default setting 1](resources/"
"quickstart/defaultsetting1.png)</div>\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-before-avoid\">![Default setting 2](resources/"
"quickstart/defaultsetting2.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- Razlage za vse elemente v **SPODNJEM MENIJU** lahko vidiš, če pritisneš in "
"držiš ime možnosti. To je na voljo tudi za večino elementov v **ZGORNJEM "
"MENIJU**.\n"
"- Celozaslonska okna (Zgodovina, Kazalo, Zaznamki, Statistika branja itd.) "
"lahko **ZAPREŠ** s podrsom navzdol.\n"
"- **ZASLONSKE SLIKE** lahko zajameš s sočasnim dotikom nasprotnih kotov "
"zaslona ali z dolgim diagonalnim podrsom.\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-after-avoid\">![Izbirnik števil](resources/"
"quickstart/numberpicker.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- V oknih s puščicami za prilagajanje (kot zgoraj) lahko gumb s puščico "
"držiš, da se vrednost spreminja hitreje.\n"
"- Okna, ki niso celozaslonska, lahko **ZAPREŠ** z dotikom izven okna. Takšna "
"okna lahko tudi **PREMIKAŠ** tako, da držiš naslovno vrstico in jo vlečeš.\n"
"- Okno lahko postane **POLPROSOJNO** (da med nastavljanjem vidiš besedilo "
"pod njim), če pritisneš in držiš naslovno vrstico okna.\n"
"- Če pritisneš in držiš besedo, se odpre okno, ki omogoča iskanje besede v "
"dokumentu ali v Wikipediji.\n"
"- Dele besedila lahko poudariš tako, da pritisneš in držiš besedo ter nato "
"vlečeš s prstom.\n"
"- Po dokumentu se lahko premikaš prek okna **HITRO PREGLEDOVANJE**:\n"
"\n"
"> **ZGORNJI MENI ➔ ![Navigacija](resources/icons/mdlight/"
"appbar.navigation.svg) ➔ Hitro pregledovanje dokumenta**\n"

#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:213
msgid ""
"## Accessing files <a id=\"afiles\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"The following methods are available for accessing your books and articles:\n"
"\n"
"* File Browser\n"
"* Favorites\n"
"* History\n"
"\n"
"You can also set KOReader to open with any of these dialogs on startup via:\n"
"\n"
"> **Menu (in File Browser) ➔ ![Filebrowser](resources/icons/mdlight/"
"appbar.filebrowser.svg) ➔ Start with**\n"
msgstr ""
"## Dostop do datotek <a id=\"afiles\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"Za dostop do tvojih knjig in člankov so na voljo naslednji načini:\n"
"\n"
"* Brskalnik datotek\n"
"* Priljubljene\n"
"* Zgodovina\n"
"\n"
"Nastaviš lahko tudi, da se KOReader ob zagonu odpre v katerem koli od teh "
"oken:\n"
"\n"
"> **Meni (v Brskalniku) ➔ ![Brskalnik](resources/icons/mdlight/"
"appbar.filebrowser.svg) ➔ Začni z**\n"

#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:227
msgid ""
"## Accessing files <a id=\"afiles\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"The following methods are available for accessing your books and articles:\n"
"\n"
"* File Browser\n"
"* Favorites\n"
"* History\n"
"\n"
"You can assign gestures for quick access to each of these dialogs.\n"
"\n"
"You can also set KOReader to open with any of these dialogs on startup via:\n"
"\n"
"> **TOP MENU (in File Browser) ➔ ![Filebrowser](resources/icons/mdlight/"
"appbar.filebrowser.svg) ➔ Start with**\n"
msgstr ""
"## Dostop do datotek <a id=\"afiles\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"Za dostop do tvojih knjig in člankov so na voljo naslednji načini:\n"
"\n"
"* Brskalnik datotek\n"
"* Priljubljene\n"
"* Zgodovina\n"
"\n"
"Za hiter dostop do vsakega od teh oken lahko določiš kretnje.\n"
"\n"
"Nastaviš lahko tudi, da se KOReader ob zagonu odpre v katerem koli od teh "
"oken:\n"
"\n"
"> **ZGORNJI MENI (v Brskalniku) ➔ ![Brskalnik](resources/icons/mdlight/"
"appbar.filebrowser.svg) ➔ Začni z**\n"

#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:245
msgid ""
"## Transferring files <a id=\"tfiles\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"In addition to transferring files the same way you would with the built-in "
"reader application, other options are available depending on your device:\n"
"\n"
"1. USB Mass Storage mode within KOReader\n"
"2. Cloud storage (Dropbox/FTP/Webdav)\n"
"3. SSH/SFTP access\n"
"4. Calibre transfer\n"
"5. News downloader\n"
"6. Wallabag\n"
msgstr ""
"## Prenos datotek <a id=\"tfiles\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"Poleg prenosa datotek na enak način kot pri tovarniškem bralniku so glede na "
"tvojo napravo na voljo še druge možnosti:\n"
"\n"
"1. Način USB masovnega pomnilnika znotraj KOReaderja\n"
"2. Shramba v oblaku (Dropbox/FTP/Webdav)\n"
"3. Dostop prek SSH/SFTP\n"
"4. Prenos prek Calibre\n"
"5. Prenašalnik novic\n"
"6. Wallabag\n"

#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:260
msgid ""
"## Shortcuts <a id=\"short\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"The following is a non-exhaustive list of shortcuts available.\n"
"\n"
"When inside the reading module:\n"
"\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Up**: Table of contents\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Right**: Add a bookmark\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Down**: Book map\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Left**: Bookmarks, notes and highlights\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Press**: Save current page to location history\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Home**: Toggle wifi on/off\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Back**: Switch to previously opened book\n"
"\n"
"When using a virtual keyboard:\n"
"\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Right**: Move cursor to right char\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Left**: Move cursor to left char\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Press**: Show special characters behind virtual keyboard "
"keys\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Home**: Toggle virtual keyboard on/off\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Back**: Delete char\n"
msgstr ""
"## Bližnjice <a id=\"short\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"Tukaj je le nekaj najpogostejših bližnjic.\n"
"\n"
"Znotraj bralnega modula:\n"
"\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Gor**: Kazalo vsebine\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Desno**: Dodaj zaznamek\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Dol**: Zemljevid knjige\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Levo**: Zaznamki, opombe in poudarki\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Press**: Shrani trenutno stran v zgodovino lokacij\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Home**: Vklop/izklop Wi-Fi-ja\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Nazaj**: Preklopi na prej odprto knjigo\n"
"\n"
"Pri uporabi navidezne tipkovnice:\n"
"\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Desno**: Premakni kazalec na desni znak\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Levo**: Premakni kazalec na levi znak\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Press**: Pokaži posebne znake za tipkami navidezne "
"tipkovnice\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Home**: Vklop/izklop navidezne tipkovnice\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Nazaj**: Izbriši znak\n"

#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:284
msgid ""
"## Shortcuts <a id=\"short\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"The following is a non-exhaustive list of shortcuts available.\n"
"\n"
"When inside the reading module:\n"
"\n"
"- **T** or **Shift** + **Up**: Table of contents\n"
"- **Shift** + **Right**: Add a bookmark\n"
"- **Shift** + **Down**: Book map\n"
"- **B** or **Shift** + **Left**: Bookmarks, notes and highlights\n"
"- **Shift** + **Press**: Save current page to location history\n"
"- **Shift** + **Home**: Toggle wifi on/off\n"
"- **Shift** + **Back**: Switch to previously opened book\n"
"\n"
"When using a virtual keyboard:\n"
"\n"
"- **Shift** + **Right**: Move cursor to right char\n"
"- **Shift** + **Left**: Move cursor to left char\n"
"- **Shift** + **Press**: Show special characters behind virtual keyboard "
"keys\n"
"- **Shift** + **Home**: Toggle virtual keyboard on/off\n"
"- **Shift** + **Del**: Delete word\n"
"- **Shift** + **Back**: Delete whole line\n"
"- **Sym** + **Alphabet keys**: symbols, numbers and special characters\n"
msgstr ""
"## Bližnjice <a id=\"short\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"Tukaj je le nekaj najpogostejših bližnjic.\n"
"\n"
"Znotraj bralnega modula:\n"
"\n"
"- **T** ali **Shift** + **Gor**: Kazalo vsebine\n"
"- **Shift** + **Desno**: Dodaj zaznamek\n"
"- **Shift** + **Dol**: Zemljevid knjige\n"
"- **B** ali **Shift** + **Levo**: Zaznamki, opombe in poudarki\n"
"- **Shift** + **Press**: Shrani trenutno stran v zgodovino lokacij\n"
"- **Shift** + **Home**: Vklop/izklop Wi-Fi-ja\n"
"- **Shift** + **Nazaj**: Preklopi na prej odprto knjigo\n"
"\n"
"Pri uporabi navidezne tipkovnice:\n"
"\n"
"- **Shift** + **Desno**: Premakni kazalec na desni znak\n"
"- **Shift** + **Levo**: Premakni kazalec na levi znak\n"
"- **Shift** + **Press**: Pokaži posebne znake za tipkami navidezne "
"tipkovnice\n"
"- **Shift** + **Home**: Vklop/izklop navidezne tipkovnice\n"
"- **Shift** + **Del**: Izbriši besedo\n"
"- **Shift** + **Nazaj**: Izbriši celo vrstico\n"
"- **Sym** + **Črkovne tipke**: simboli, številke in posebni znaki\n"

#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:310
msgid ""
"## Frontlight/backlight <a id=\"flight\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"You can control your screen light via this menu. If you have warm lighting "
"(normal white LEDs+orange ones) you can control them separately from this "
"dialog:\n"
"\n"
"> **TOP MENU ➔ ![Settings](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.settings.svg) ➔ "
"Frontlight**\n"
msgstr ""
"## Osvetlitev zaslona <a id=\"flight\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"Osvetlitev zaslona lahko upravljaš v tem meniju. Če imaš napravo s toplo "
"svetlobo (bele + oranžne LED-diode), ju lahko v tem oknu nastavljaš ločeno:\n"
"\n"
"> **ZGORNJI MENI ➔ ![Nastavitve](resources/icons/mdlight/"
"appbar.settings.svg) ➔ Osvetlitev**\n"

#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:320
msgid ""
"## While reading <a id=\"reading\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"table\"><div>\n"
"\n"
"You can change the font\n"
"\n"
"**TOP MENU ➔ ![Typesettings](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.typeset.svg) ➔ "
"Font**\n"
"\n"
"</div><div>\n"
"\n"
"Make font bigger\n"
"\n"
"**BOTTOM MENU ➔ ![Textsize](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.textsize.svg)**\n"
"\n"
"</div><div>\n"
"\n"
"Make font bolder\n"
"\n"
"**BOTTOM MENU ➔ ![Contrast](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.contrast.svg)**\n"
"\n"
"</div><div>\n"
"\n"
"Invert the colors (white text on black)\n"
"\n"
"**TOP MENU ➔ ![Settings](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.settings.svg) ➔ "
"Night mode**\n"
"\n"
"</div><div>\n"
"\n"
"Change many formatting options\n"
"\n"
"**TOP MENU ➔ ![Typesettings](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.typeset.svg) ➔ "
"Style tweaks**\n"
"\n"
"</div></div>\n"
msgstr ""
"## Med branjem <a id=\"reading\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"table\"><div>\n"
"\n"
"Spremeni pisavo\n"
"\n"
"**ZGORNJI MENI ➔ ![Oblikovanje](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.typeset.svg) "
"➔ Pisava**\n"
"\n"
"</div><div>\n"
"\n"
"Povečaj pisavo\n"
"\n"
"**SPODNJI MENI ➔ ![Velikost besedila](resources/icons/mdlight/"
"appbar.textsize.svg)**\n"
"\n"
"</div><div>\n"
"\n"
"Podebelaj pisavo\n"
"\n"
"**SPODNJI MENI ➔ ![Kontrast](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.contrast.svg)**\n"
"\n"
"</div><div>\n"
"\n"
"Obrni barve (belo besedilo na črnem)\n"
"\n"
"**ZGORNJI MENI ➔ ![Nastavitve](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.settings.svg) "
"➔ Nočni način**\n"
"\n"
"</div><div>\n"
"\n"
"Prilagodi slog in oblikovanje\n"
"\n"
"**ZGORNJI MENI ➔ ![Oblikovanje](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.typeset.svg) "
"➔ Slogovni popravki**\n"
"\n"
"</div></div>\n"

#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:357
msgid ""
"## Installing dictionaries <a id=\"dicts\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"KOReader supports dictionary lookup in EPUB and even in scanned PDF/DJVU "
"documents. To see the dictionary definition or translation, tap and hold a "
"word.\n"
"\n"
"To use the dictionary lookup function, first you need to install one or more "
"dictionaries in the StarDict format. KOReader has an inbuilt dictionary "
"installation system:\n"
"\n"
"**TOP MENU ➔ ![Search](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.search.svg) ➔ "
"Dictionary Settings > Download dictionaries**\n"
msgstr ""
"## Namestitev slovarjev <a id=\"dicts\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"KOReader podpira iskanje v slovarju v formatih EPUB in celo v skeniranih "
"dokumentih PDF/DJVU. Za prikaz definicije ali prevoda pritisni in drži "
"besedo.\n"
"\n"
"Za uporabo te funkcije moraš najprej namestiti enega ali več slovarjev v "
"formatu StarDict. KOReader ima vgrajen sistem za namestitev slovarjev:\n"
"\n"
"**ZGORNJI MENI ➔ ![Iskanje](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.search.svg) ➔ "
"Nastavitve slovarja > Prenesi slovarje**\n"

