#: frontend/ui/widget/bookmapwidget.lua:1504
msgid ""
"Book map provides a summary of a book's content, showing chapters and pages "
"visually. If statistics are enabled, black bars represent pages already read "
"(gray for pages read in the current session), with varying heights based on "
"reading time.\n"
"\n"
"Map legend:\n"
"▲ current page\n"
"❶ ❷ … previous locations\n"
"① ② … next locations\n"
"▒ highlighted text\n"
" highlighted text with notes\n"
" bookmarked page\n"
" pinned page\n"
"▢ focused page when coming from Pages browser"
msgstr ""
"Zemljevid knjige ponuja povzetek vsebine, ki vizualno prikazuje poglavja in "
"strani. Če je omogočena statistika, črne črtice predstavljajo že prebrane "
"strani (sive pa strani, prebrane v trenutni seji), višina črtic pa je "
"odvisna od časa branja.\n"
"\n"
"Legenda:\n"
"▲ trenutna stran\n"
"❶ ❷ … prejšnje lokacije\n"
"① ② … naslednje lokacije\n"
"▒ poudarjeno besedilo\n"
" poudarjeno besedilo z opombami\n"
" stran z zaznamkom\n"
" pripeta stran\n"
"▢ stran v fokusu ob prihodu iz brskalnika strani"

#: frontend/ui/widget/bookmapwidget.lua:1518
msgid ""
"When in overview mode, the book map is always displayed in grid mode to fit "
"on one screen. The chapter levels can be easily adjusted for the most "
"convenient overview experience."
msgstr ""
"V načinu pregleda je zemljevid knjige vedno prikazan v mrežnem načinu, da se "
"prilega enemu zaslonu. Ravni poglavij lahko poljubno prilagodiš za najboljšo "
"preglednost."

#: frontend/ui/widget/bookmapwidget.lua:1521
msgid ""
"When you first open a book, the book map will begin in grid mode, displaying "
"all chapter levels on one screen for a comprehensive overview of the book's "
"content."
msgstr ""
"Ko prvič odpreš knjigo, se bo zemljevid knjige prikazal v mrežnem načinu z "
"vsemi ravnmi poglavij za celovit pregled vsebine."

#: frontend/ui/widget/bookmapwidget.lua:1530
msgid ""
"Use settings in this menu to change the level of chapters to include in the "
"book map, the view type (grid or flat) and the width of page slots.\n"
"\n"
"Use \"ScreenKB/Shift\" + \"Up/Down\" to scroll or use the page turn buttons "
"to move at a faster rate.\n"
"\n"
"Press back to exit the book map."
msgstr ""
"Uporabi nastavitve v tem meniju za spreminjanje ravni poglavij v zemljevidu, "
"vrste pogleda (mrežni ali ploski) in širine polj strani.\n"
"\n"
"Za pomikanje uporabi \"ScreenKB/Shift\" + \"Gor/Dol\" ali gumba za obračanje "
"strani za hitrejši premik.\n"
"\n"
"Pritisni nazaj za izhod iz zemljevida."

#: frontend/ui/widget/bookmapwidget.lua:1537
msgid ""
"Tap on a location in the book to browse thumbnails of the pages there.\n"
"\n"
"Swipe along the left screen edge to change the level of chapters to include "
"in the book map.\n"
"\n"
"Any multiswipe will close the book map."
msgstr ""
"Dotakni se lokacije v knjigi za brskanje po sličicah strani na tem mestu.\n"
"\n"
"Podrsaj ob levem robu zaslona za spreminjanje ravni poglavij v zemljevidu.\n"
"\n"
"Katera koli kretnja z več prsti bo zaprla zemljevid."

#: frontend/ui/widget/bookmapwidget.lua:1544
msgid ""
"Tap on a location in the book to browse thumbnails of the pages there.\n"
"\n"
"Swipe along the left screen edge to change the level of chapters to include "
"in the book map, and the type of book map (grid or flat) when crossing the "
"level 0.\n"
"\n"
"Swipe along the bottom screen edge to change the width of page slots.\n"
"\n"
"Swipe or pan vertically on content to scroll.\n"
"\n"
"Long-press on ≡ to switch between current and initial views.\n"
"\n"
"Any multiswipe will close the book map."
msgstr ""
"Dotakni se lokacije v knjigi za brskanje po sličicah strani.\n"
"\n"
"Podrsaj ob levem robu zaslona za spreminjanje ravni poglavij in vrste "
"pogleda (mrežni/ploski) ob prehodu ravni 0.\n"
"\n"
"Podrsaj ob spodnjem robu zaslona za spreminjanje širine polj strani.\n"
"\n"
"Za pomikanje podrsaj navpično po vsebini.\n"
"\n"
"Dolgo pritisni na ≡ za preklop med trenutnim in začetnim pogledom.\n"
"\n"
"Katera koli kretnja z več prsti bo zaprla zemljevid."

