#: frontend/ui/widget/pagebrowserwidget.lua:1147
msgid ""
"Page browser shows thumbnails of a book's pages.\n"
"\n"
"The bottom ribbon displays an extract of the book map around the pages "
"displayed:\n"
"\n"
"If statistics are enabled, black bars indicate pages that have already been "
"read (gray bars for pages read in the current session). The height of these "
"bars varies based on the time spent reading each page.\n"
"Chapters are indicated above the pages they cover.\n"
"Below the pages, the following indicators may appear:\n"
"▲ current page\n"
"❶ ❷ … previous locations\n"
"① ② … next locations\n"
"▒ highlighted text\n"
" highlighted text with notes\n"
" bookmarked page\n"
" pinned page"
msgstr ""
"Brskalnik strani prikazuje sličice strani v knjigi.\n"
"\n"
"V spodnjem traku je prikazan izseček zemljevida knjige okoli trenutnih "
"strani:\n"
"\n"
"Če je statistika omogočena, črne črtice označujejo že prebrane strani (sive "
"pa strani, prebrane v trenutni seji). Višina črtic je odvisna od časa, "
"porabljenega za posamezno stran.\n"
"Poglavja so označena nad stranmi, ki jih obsegajo.\n"
"Pod stranmi se lahko pojavijo naslednji indikatorji:\n"
"▲ trenutna stran\n"
"❶ ❷ … prejšnje lokacije\n"
"① ② … naslednje lokacije\n"
"▒ poudarjeno besedilo\n"
" poudarjeno besedilo z opombami\n"
" stran z zaznamkom\n"
" pripeta stran"

#: frontend/ui/widget/pagebrowserwidget.lua:1168
msgid ""
"Swipe along the top or left screen edge to change the number of columns or "
"rows of thumbnails.\n"
"\n"
"Swipe vertically to move one row, horizontally to move one screen.\n"
"\n"
"Swipe horizontally in the bottom ribbon to move by the full stripe.\n"
"\n"
"Tap in the bottom ribbon on a page to focus thumbnails on this page.\n"
"\n"
"Tap on a thumbnail to read that page.\n"
"\n"
"Long-press on ≡ to decrease or reset the number of chapter levels shown in "
"the bottom ribbon.\n"
"\n"
"Any multiswipe will close the page browser."
msgstr ""
"Podrsaj ob zgornjem ali levem robu zaslona, da spremeniš število stolpcev "
"ali vrstic sličic.\n"
"\n"
"Podrsaj navpično za premik za eno vrstico, vodoravno pa za premik za en "
"zaslon.\n"
"\n"
"V spodnjem traku podrsaj vodoravno za premik za celoten trak.\n"
"\n"
"V spodnjem traku se dotakni strani, da osredotočiš sličice na to stran.\n"
"\n"
"Dotakni se sličice, da začneš brati to stran.\n"
"\n"
"Dolgo pritisni na ≡, da zmanjšaš ali ponastaviš število ravni poglavij v "
"spodnjem traku.\n"
"\n"
"Katera koli kretnja z več prsti zapre brskalnik strani."

#: frontend/ui/widget/pagebrowserwidget.lua:1184
#: frontend/ui/widget/pagebrowserwidget.lua:1194
msgid ""
"The settings (in this menu) can be used to change the number of rows and "
"columns, whether to display page numbers, and to display different chapter-"
"levels in the bottom ribbon."
msgstr ""
"Z nastavitvami (v tem meniju) lahko spremeniš število vrstic in stolpcev, "
"vklopiš prikaz številk strani ali spremeniš prikaz ravni poglavij v spodnjem "
"traku."

