#: plugins/coverimage.koplugin/main.lua:472
msgid ""
"This plugin saves a book cover to a file. That file can then be used as a "
"screensaver on certain devices.\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the cover image of the current file is stored in the set path on "
"book opening. Books can be excluded if desired.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, the cover file will be deleted.\n"
"\n"
"If fallback is enabled, the fallback file will be copied to the screensaver "
"file on book closing.\n"
"If the filename is empty or the file doesn't exist, the cover file will be "
"deleted.\n"
"\n"
"If fallback is disabled, the screensaver image will stay in place after "
"closing a book."
msgstr ""
"Ta vtičnik shrani naslovnico knjige v datoteko. To datoteko lahko na "
"nekaterih napravah uporabiš kot ohranjevalnik zaslona.\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočeno, se slika naslovnice trenutne knjige ob odpiranju shrani na "
"določeno pot. Če želiš, lahko nekatere knjige izključiš.\n"
"\n"
"Če je onemogočeno, bo datoteka naslovnice izbrisana.\n"
"\n"
"Če je omogočena nadomestna slika, se bo ta ob zapiranju knjige kopirala v "
"datoteko ohranjevalnika zaslona.\n"
"Če je ime datoteke prazno ali datoteka ne obstaja, bo datoteka naslovnice "
"izbrisana.\n"
"\n"
"Če je nadomestna slika onemogočena, bo slika ohranjevalnika zaslona po "
"zaprtju knjige ostala nespremenjena."

