#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:693
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:697
msgid "Tap interval"
msgstr "Interval dotika"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:698
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:725
msgid ""
"Any other taps made within this interval after a first tap will be "
"considered accidental and ignored.\n"
"\n"
"The interval value is in milliseconds and can range from 0 (0 seconds) to "
"2000 (2 seconds)."
msgstr ""
"Vsi ostali dotiki v tem intervalu po prvem dotiku bodo obravnavani kot "
"naključni in prezrti.\n"
"\n"
"Vrednost intervala je v milisekundah in je lahko od 0 (0 sekund) do 2000 (2 "
"sekundi)."

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:720
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:724
msgid "Tap interval on keyboard"
msgstr "Interval dotika na tipkovnici"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:746
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:750
msgid "Double tap interval"
msgstr "Interval dvojnega dotika"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:751
msgid ""
"When double tap is enabled, this sets the time to wait for the second tap. A "
"single tap will take at least this long to be detected.\n"
"\n"
"The interval value is in milliseconds and can range from 100 (0.1 seconds) "
"to 2000 (2 seconds)."
msgstr ""
"Ko je dvojni dotik omogočen, to določa čas čakanja na drugi dotik. Zaznava "
"enojnega dotika bo trajala vsaj toliko časa.\n"
"\n"
"Vrednost intervala je v milisekundah in je lahko od 100 (0,1 sekunde) do "
"2000 (2 sekundi)."

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:773
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:777
msgid "Two finger tap duration"
msgstr "Trajanje dotika z dvema prstoma"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:778
msgid ""
"This sets the allowed duration of any of the two fingers touch/release for "
"the combined event to be considered a two finger tap.\n"
"\n"
"The duration value is in milliseconds and can range from 100 (0.1 seconds) "
"to 2000 (2 seconds)."
msgstr ""
"Določa dovoljeno trajanje dotika/izpusta kateregakoli od dveh prstov, da se "
"dogodek šteje za dotik z dvema prstoma.\n"
"\n"
"Vrednost trajanja je v milisekundah in je lahko od 100 (0,1 sekunde) do 2000 "
"(2 sekundi)."

